175
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, he went back to his shop.</font>

176
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He says he was able to vent a lot of 
his curses on that recent investigation.</font>

177
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he had to take a page from</font>

178
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san and focus on his business.</font>

179
00:12:58,580 --> 00:13:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were awesome back there, Tonome-chan!</font>

180
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gotta work hard, too!</font>

181
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right.</font>

182
00:13:04,170 --> 00:13:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that guy? Sheesh.</font>

183
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you mind if I ask you a question?</font>

184
00:13:14,860 --> 00:13:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

185
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What led to you and 
Madaraito-san living together?</font>

186
00:13:22,610 --> 00:13:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought it'd be a question about work.</font>

187
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EARNEST</font>

188
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Efficiency.</font>

189
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a very long wait 
for a very simple answer!</font>

190
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't talk to me about stuff like that.</font>

191
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's like a work mindset thing.</font>

192
00:13:48,210 --> 00:13:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Detective stuff means extracting 
info from someone else,</font>

193
00:13:51,990 --> 00:13:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm guarded about revealing 
my personal info to others.</font>

194
00:13:56,330 --> 00:13:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're embarrassed?</font>

195
00:13:58,050 --> 00:14:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up. You can't just ask that.</font>

196
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just hoping to get some info 
for personal reference.</font>

197
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

198
00:14:07,230 --> 00:14:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll ask Madaraito-san and—</font>

199
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't ask that blabbermouth anything!</font>

200
00:14:12,740 --> 00:14:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason we started living 
together is because Daichi—</font>

201
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

202
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you guys are gonna
move in together?</font>

203
00:14:23,810 --> 00:14:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

204
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I don't think our experience 
is gonna be any help to you.</font>

205
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want practical 
advice on cohabiting.</font>

206
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asking something like that means you've 
got something specific on your mind.</font>

207
00:14:39,470 --> 00:14:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's true...</font>

208
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonome-san is just so amazing!</font>

209
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you're just bragging.</font>

210
00:14:46,770 --> 00:14:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just...</font>

211
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's <i>too</i> amazing. I keep thinking 
I'll end up totally dependent on him...</font>

212
00:14:53,850 --> 00:14:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think he's too accommodating of you?</font>

213
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:59,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! It feels like something like that!</font>

214
00:14:59,590 --> 00:15:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So tell him to stop?</font>

215
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:04,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though he's amazing?</font>

216
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speak up or put a stop to it, 
and restore some balance.</font>

217
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though, I can't promise it'll end 
up in your ideal form at the end.</font>

218
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

219
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}STONE-BAKED SWEET POTATOES</font>

220
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you are!</font>

221
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

222
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome!</font>

223
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

224
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san. I brought you back 
a baked sweet potato!</font>

225
00:15:30,010 --> 00:15:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't had one in so long!</font>

226
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we split it?</font>

227
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here!</font>

228
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:43,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

229
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}What was that "ah" about?</i></font>

230
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you mind if I check your sweet potato?</font>

231
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Certainly.</font>

232
00:15:52,110 --> 00:15:54,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just messed up splitting it.</font>

233
00:15:56,100 --> 00:15:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

234
00:15:58,420 --> 00:16:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You took advantage of my blindness!</font>

235
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You rotten SD!</font>

236
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going back to cut it!</font>

237
00:16:06,990 --> 00:16:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S...?</font>

238
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kikira-san.</font>

239
00:16:11,070 --> 00:16:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's an SD?</font>

240
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:14,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No idea.</font>

241
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san, I'm sorry.</font>

242
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was acting really selfishly earlier.</font>

243
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About that...</font>

244
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been evaluating me too highly!</font>

245
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kikira-san told me everything.</font>

246
00:16:36,130 --> 00:16:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">SD? Look it up yourself.</font>

247
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... I partly want to know 
the definition, but...</font>

248
00:16:44,690 --> 00:16:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was hoping I could talk about it, too...</font>

249
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're both exhausting.</font>

250
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:58,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">SD is short for "super darling."</font>

251
00:16:58,550 --> 00:16:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Super...?</font>

252
00:16:59,930 --> 00:17:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In certain circles, 
it's used to refer to a desirable,</font>

253
00:17:04,170 --> 00:17:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">mature, perpetually smooth, perfect man.</font>

254
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perfect? Me?</font>

255
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has an excellent education, 
he's tall, he has a good income.</font>

256
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:18,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he's also kind, from a good family, 
attractive, and good at housework.</font>

257
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Common SDs with all those 
traits include wealthy heirs...</font>

258
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm a wealthy heir!</font>

259
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">CEOs...</font>

260
00:17:26,070 --> 00:17:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CEO!</font>

261
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And oil barons...</font>

262
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm an oil baron!</font>

263
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san,</font>

264
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you shouldn't assume things
just because I'm invisible.</font>

265
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So humble! Amazing!</font>

266
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I being too accommodating with you?</font>

267
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean...</font>

268
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's selfish to complain 
about you caring about me, right?!</font>

269
00:17:55,020 --> 00:17:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget I said anything!</font>

270
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it takes courage 
to be honest about these things.</font>

271
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

272
00:18:00,390 --> 00:18:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not at all...</font>

273
00:18:02,930 --> 00:18:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}He's even trying 
to reassure me... He's so kind...</i></font>

274
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's not because I'm an "SD" 
or anything like that.</font>

275
00:18:11,510 --> 00:18:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to earn your trust.</font>

276
00:18:17,320 --> 00:18:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

277
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on... You think I don't trust you?</font>

278
00:18:22,700 --> 00:18:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's nothing like that.</font>

279
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's more...</font>

280
00:18:30,790 --> 00:18:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there a reason it's 
hard to talk about?</font>

281
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just,</font>

282
00:18:34,130 --> 00:18:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to make 
excuses for my behavior</font>

283
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when you're already feeling anxious...</font>

284
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is just what I'm talking about!</font>

285
00:18:41,420 --> 00:18:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, right. I'm sorry.</font>

286
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a long time, invisible 
people mostly worked as spies</font>

287
00:18:50,470 --> 00:18:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and other secretive professions.</font>

288
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many of us have few 
records of our past,</font>

289
00:18:57,940 --> 00:18:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and don't know our roots.</font>

290
00:19:01,710 --> 00:19:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our invisibility was considered useful,</font>

291
00:19:04,360 --> 00:19:08,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's hard for us, as a race, 
to establish trust with others.</font>

292
00:19:10,100 --> 00:19:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I was young, too, 
I was tutored on how to act.</font>

293
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was like... Tips about blending 
into normal society.</font>

294
00:19:20,250 --> 00:19:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder why that is.</font>

295
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only thing that makes you different 
is that you're invisible, right?</font>

296
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why does that make it hard 
for people to trust you?</font>

297
00:19:31,870 --> 00:19:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The <i>only thing</i> that makes us different?</font>

298
00:19:36,690 --> 00:19:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess, from your perspective, 
that's not a big difference at all, is it?</font>

299
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really sorry.</font>

300
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. It makes me happy.</font>

301
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

302
00:19:48,990 --> 00:19:55,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does being invisible make life hard 
for most invisible people?</font>

303
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few years back,</font>

304
00:19:58,360 --> 00:20:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">an invisible fashion 
model appeared on the scene.</font>

305
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He incorporated his 
invisibility into his looks</font>

306
00:20:04,050 --> 00:20:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and became the talk of the industry.</font>

307
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It put the existence of invisible 
people into the spotlight</font>

308
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and helped people understand us.</font>

309
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were invisible models really that rare?</font>

310
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think he was the first 
invisible model ever,</font>

311
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">though he's retired now.</font>

312
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meeting him when I was a child saved me.</font>

313
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know him?!</font>

314
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

315
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's part of the reason I started 
using clothing to express myself.</font>

316
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:37,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's like a big brother 
to me, and a friend.</font>

317
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know you had 
an inspiration like that!</font>

318
00:20:43,180 --> 00:20:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I'll try to be a little 
less overly accommodating with you.</font>

319
00:20:46,770 --> 00:20:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll start with...</font>

320
00:20:49,280 --> 00:20:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Devouring this donut 
right in front of you!</font>

321
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Starting there, hmm?</font>

322
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Another sleepover!</i></font>

323
00:21:04,560 --> 00:21:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I was nervous at first,</i></font>

324
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but Akira-san's been acted so normal, 
I'm really getting used to it!</i></font>

325
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}And here I was,</i></font>

326
00:21:14,930 --> 00:21:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>hoping for even more 
canoodling than before!</i></font>

327
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}What do you mean, even more canoodling?!</i></font>

328
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Is it kind of a let-down?</i></font>

329
00:21:41,450 --> 00:21:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}It's hard for invisible people 
to earn trust with others...</i></font>

330
00:21:48,670 --> 00:21:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I couldn't tell her the real reason.</i></font>

331
00:21:52,730 --> 00:21:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I've got to tell her properly sometime.</i></font>

332
00:21:59,130 --> 00:22:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I really don't want to.</i></font>

333
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"></font>

334
00:22:07,050 --> 00:22:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 8: I GUESS I'M BEING SELFISH
TO BE CONTINUED</font>

